@startuml impl_cmp_01_package_layers
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80
title IMPL-CMP-01 - Package e dipendenze Python
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "acl.adapters.requests" as ReqAdapters
component "acl.adapters.identity" as IdentityAdapters
component "acl.bootstrap" as Bootstrap
component "acl.infrastructure" as Infra
component "acl.application" as App
component "acl.ports" as Ports
component "acl.domain" as Domain

ReqAdapters --> App
ReqAdapters --> IdentityAdapters
IdentityAdapters --> Ports
Bootstrap --> App
Bootstrap --> Infra
Bootstrap --> Ports
Infra ..|> Ports
Infra --> Domain
App --> Ports
App --> Domain
Ports --> Domain

note bottom of Domain
  Domain non importa mai application, ports,
  infrastructure, adapters o config runtime.
end note

note right of Bootstrap
  Composition root:
  assembla implementazioni concrete
  con dependency injection esplicita.
end note

legend
  Vedi anche: [[../classi/01_domain_objects.puml Domain]] |
  [[../classi/03_ports_adapters.puml Porte/adapter]]
endlegend
@enduml
